      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to rescind funds appropriated by the  Consolidated Appropriations Act, 2008, for the City of Berkeley, California, and any entities located in such city, and to provide that such funds shall be transferred to the Operation and Maintenance, Marine Corps account of the Department of Defense for the purposes of recruiting.</title>
